data.description: Lovely 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home located in a quiet neighborhood near Ft Liberty! As you enter the formal dining room your breath will be taken away by the custom woodwork on the ceilings and the Wainscoting on the walls. The kitchen features new granite countertops and stainless appliances. The kitchen leads into a spacious family room with a cozy fireplace. There is a half bath conveniently located on the first floor. Upstairs you will find two spacious bedrooms, laundry room and primary suite. In the primary suite there are French doors that lead into your own spacious retreat! Beautiful ensuite bath and large walk in closet. This home is a must see! 29 minutes to Fayetteville, 36 minutes to Sanford, 58 minutes to Apex, 69 minutes to RTP, 43 minutes to Raleigh Executive Jetport.
